{"tid":155460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[天收廢老]梅媽遭申請破產","createTime":"2017-03-14T05:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T08:23:30.000Z","uid":77196,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ffa80ecdcb8c4649e4b136eceb2d2d0d2a3fa1","tid":155460,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:12:53.000Z","msg":"已故樂壇天后梅艷芳的母親梅媽覃美金，為一次過取得梅艷芳的遺產而屢次興訟，最終因爭產失敗兼欠下訟費，於2012年被頒下破產令，直至去年4月，梅媽的破產令始獲解除。惟梅媽日前<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>再遭兩名曾任其破產受託人的會計師Wong Teck Meng及Chan Pui Sze入稟高院申請破產</strong></span>，入稟狀未有透露詳情，案件已排期於5月10日處理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解佢仲未去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279fa4eb66d092a1f06d5247bce6b7a20849b20c","tid":155460,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:18:00.000Z","msg":"幾億身家咁就敗哂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可悲"},{"pid":"21eb142d6cb612f54278db8f43799708c98c0028","tid":155460,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:18:21.000Z","msg":"比1千萬我都有排咬啦"},{"pid":"d897780c80c87383d19289e97fcf45f2e073b199","tid":155460,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:19:20.000Z","msg":"又出嚟話被迫害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b44c9bd70f28c1fa0cf495268d6947ba5cbbcb6","tid":155460,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比1千萬我都有排咬啦</blockquote><br />\n1千萬 買完層樓 做M記都得喇"},{"pid":"03b626a42b7d2f91accfae6f73c000a60948bc52","tid":155460,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"梅艷芳的遺產的確係判比佢老母<br />\n<br />\n人地啲錢點駛, 關人鬼事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4a6487bdf5bf5397b10a3166829f5c649afee4","tid":155460,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梅艷芳的遺產的確係判比佢老母<br />\n<br />\n人地啲錢點駛, 關人鬼事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n件廢老想食埋其他人果份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5c524feacd5b91f9a82ee446d2bfb62d158cc8","tid":155460,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:45:22.000Z","msg":"件廢老想食埋其他人果份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n咁都係梅艷芳既遺產, 佢老母有權去提出訴訟<br />\n佢個仆街老母想要多啲錢洗, 其實有咩問題<br />\n香港人個個都貪婪<br />\n<br />\n佢老母比啲傳媒話佢點大洗點貪錢點嗜賭如命, 其實又點姐<br />\n人地點洗錢, 唔關人事<br />\n<br />\n我覺得1億好多好多, 也許好多人地唔係"},{"pid":"5198084561a4aba902ade8ec5013b0651e3ebc99","tid":155460,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:51:06.000Z","msg":"班垃圾mk 合理化隻廢老貪心"},{"pid":"607f2ba570f8f48fa0bc7e458e6c2a153902e159","tid":155460,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"個律師真係大贏家"},{"pid":"857e2b73048f911bae8ab1ce0fb8121859238f73","tid":155460,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"佢個仔叫佢出黎姐"},{"pid":"f74d9e5a1d2e897a1f90629a081f3cb3816b7e16","tid":155460,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:54:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班垃圾mk 合理化隻廢老貪心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貪心貪錢有咩問題呀, 有咩罪呢<br />\n佢又係去打訴訟, 正路架喎<br />\n<br />\n啲錢又唔係其它人既, 政府錢又話姐<br />\n<br />\n人貪錢就緊架喇"},{"pid":"84004aad880ac84d963d74840a04054636fcba88","tid":155460,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:56:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>件廢老想食埋其他人果份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f